<h1>
  coi
  <small class="translation">Hello!</small>
</h1>
<h2>
  <b>Lojban</b> is a <b>constructed</b>, <b>syntactically unambiguous</b> human language created to reflect the principles of <b>logic</b>.
</h2>
<p>
  Lojban is <b>phonetically unambiguous</b>, meaning that every sound corresponds to a single letter. Lojban has no special characters such as quotation marks or parenthesis. Any lojban statement can be written using only the twenty-four characters of the lojban alphabet.
</p>
<p>The Lojban alphabet is like English, with a few rules and exceptions.</p>
  <p>
    <b>a</b> as in palm,
    <b>e</b> as in get,
    <b>i</b> as in machine,
    <b>o</b> as in more,
    <b>u</b> as in tube,
    <b>y</b> like the u in fun,
  </p>
  <p>
    <b>c</b> like the sh in shop,
    <b>g</b> as in gum,
    <b>j</b> like the s in treasure,
    <b>x</b> like the ch in Bach,
  </p>
  <p>
    <b>'</b> as a short h sound,
    and <b>.</b> as a short pause.
  </p>
<p>Lojban is <b>lexically unambiguous</b>, meaning that each word has a distinct meaning, spelling and pronunciation. Lojban has no synonyms, homographs, or homophones.</p>
<div class="examples">
  <p>
    <span class="example">👍</span>
    drani
    <small class="translation">right</small>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span class="example">📐</span>
    kurfa
    <small class="translation">right</small>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span class="example">➡️</span>
    pritu
    <small class="translation">right</small>
  </p>
</div>
<p>
  Lojban is <b>syntactically unambiguous</b>, meaning that any sentence can be interpreted only one way. Instead of prepositions, Lojban relies on the order of words to determine their relation.
</p>
<div class="examples">
  <div class="line">
    <p class="center">
    <b>tavla:</b>
    <span class="translation">
      <span style="color:green;"><i>X</i></span>
      <span>talks/speaks to</span>
      <span style="color:navy;"><i>X</i></span>
      <span>about subject</span>
      <span style="color:olive;"><i>X</i></span>
      <span>in language</span>
      <span style="color:purple;"><i>X</i></span>
    </span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="line">
    <p class="center">
      <span style="color:green;">mi</span>
      <span><b>tavla</b></span>
      <span style="color:navy;">do</span>
      <span style="color:olive;">lo badna</span>
      <span style="color:purple;">lo jbobau</span>
      <small class="translation">
        <span style="color:green;">I</span>
        <span><b>talk</b></span>
        <span>to</span>
        <span style="color:navy;">you</span>
        <span>about</span>
        <span style="color:olive;">bananas</span>
        <span>in</span>
        <span style="color:purple;">Lojban</span>.
      </small>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<p>
  Lojban pronouns have no default <b>case</b>, <b>animacy</b>, or <b>gender</b>.
</p>
<div class="examples">
  <div class="line">
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">👆</span>
      mi
      <small class="translation">I</small>
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">🙋</span>
      mi
      <small class="translation">me</small>
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">👪</span>
      mi
      <small class="translation">us</small>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="line">
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">👩</span>
      ta
      <small class="translation">her</small>
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">👨</span>
      ta
      <small class="translation">him</small>
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">📺</span>
      ta
      <small class="translation">it</small>
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">🐑🐑🐑</span>
      ta
      <small class="translation">they</small>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<p>
Neither do they have default <b>number</b> or <b>tense</b>.
</p>
<div class="examples">
  <div class="line">
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">
        <%= image_tag("willjump.jpg", size: "25x50") %>
      </span>
      plipe
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">
        <%= image_tag("jumping.jpg", size: "25x50") %>
      </span>
      plipe
    </p>
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">
        <%= image_tag("jumped.jpg", size: "25x50") %>
      </span>
      plipe
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="line">
    <p class="center">
      <span class="example">🐕</span>
